'''[[umbilical]] [[cord]]'''

# {{anatomy}} The [[flexible]] [[structure]] [[connecting]] a [[foetus]] with the [[placenta]]; which [[transport]]s [[nourishment]] to the [[foetus]] and [[remove]]s [[waste]].
#(''aerospace'') The [[line]] that [[supplies]] an [[astronaut]] with [[oxygen]] and [[communication]]s when [[outside]] a [[spacecraft]]
#(''aerospace'') any of the various lines connecting a [[rocket]] to its [[launch pad]] before [[liftoff]]

